                        <a href="~/howtopost.mp4" target="_blank" class="btn btn-primary" style="margin-top:5px;">Video on How to Pick Koboview Advert</a>
                       
                        <a href="~/uploadproof.mp4" target="_blank" class="btn btn-primary" style="margin-top:5px;">Video on How to Upload Video Proof</a>
