                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="col-md-4 col-sm-4 col-12">
                    <div class="feature-box-long">

                        <h3>Clients</h3>
                        <h6>Maximize Your Reach with KoboView!</h6>
                        <p>Are you looking to boost your brand's visibility on WhatsApp? Partner with KoboView: </p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>
                                <strong>Tailored Advertising Solutions: </strong>
                                Leverage KoboView's precision targeting to reach your ideal audience. Craft compelling ads and watch as they captivate thousands on WhatsApp.
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <strong> Transparent Pricing:</strong>
                                Know exactly where your investment goes. Our affordable pricing ensures you get the best value for your advertising budget.
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <strong>Real-time Analytics:</strong>

                                Gain valuable insights into your campaign's performance. Track views, engagement, and more to refine your strategy and optimize results.
                            </li>

                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>
